title: AnubisDAO RUG has been around for a long time. No progress has been made so far. The liar took 13000eth, which was very arrogant
body:
1. Choose to continue to wait, let the scammers be arrogant and don't want money anymore.
2. Let the scammer pay back the money. If legal means cannot solve the problem, then we victims will raise some funds and let the scammer suffer unintended consequences!
